rows.label: qst002904_msg0001
rows.name: The request is now complete, mo.

rows.label: qst002904_msg0002
rows.name:
I thought I was tricked by the
Superbian army, but I got all sorts
of things, so it all evens out, mo.

rows.label: qst002904_msg0003
rows.name:
Tsubutsubu and the others
will continue to sell useful
things to you all here, mo.

rows.label: qst002904_msg0004
rows.name:
We look forward to your
continued patronage, mo.

rows.label: qst002904_msg0101
rows.name:
It seems Tsubutsubu's request
is also complete, mo.

rows.label: qst002904_msg0102
rows.name:
She loves honey so much,
she looked so happy, mo.

rows.label: qst002904_msg0103
rows.name:
Thank you for listening to my
selfish sister's wish, mo.

rows.label: qst002904_msg0201
rows.name:
Tsubutsubu's request is
not yet complete, mo.

rows.label: qst002904_msg0202
rows.name:
She's a selfish little
sister, but I'd really like
you to grant her wish, mo.

rows.label: qst002904_msg0203
rows.name: I will pay you properly, mo.
